---
// CV section component
---

<div class="py-20 bg-warm-50 dark:bg-primary-900">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-6">
      Curriculum Vitae
    </h2>
    <p class="text-xl text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Download my CV to learn more about my professional experience, skills, and achievements.
    </p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-primary-800 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-primary-200 dark:border-primary-700">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-6">
          Professional Summary
        </h3>
        <ul class="text-left space-y-3 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            <span>strong foundation in SEO, AI optimization, and generative engine optimization (GEO/AIO)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            <span>proven results: 12x impressions, 5x clicks, and 5x backlinks in 3 months</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            <span>founder experience building AI-driven SEO agency and transitioning it to SaaS</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            <span>experience leading growth, strategy, and technical execution in early-stage startups</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-accent-600 rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
            <span>track record of winning global startup competitions and delivering high-impact projects</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-accent-50 dark:bg-accent-900/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-accent-200 dark:border-accent-800">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-accent-600 rounded-2xl mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-900 dark:text-primary-100 mb-4">
            Download Complete CV
          </h3>
          <p class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 mb-6">
            Get the full details about my professional journey, technical skills, and project portfolio.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/cv.pdf" 
            download 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-accent-600 hover:bg-accent-700 text-white rounded-lg transition-colors font-medium"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
            Download CV (PDF)
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-sm text-primary-500 dark:text-primary-400">
          <p>Last updated: July 2025</p>
          <p>File size: ~88KB</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div> 